snippet.title: URBAN RIVALS WORLD - full anime teaser
snippet.description:
It feels like a 30 seconds dream for us, that we can finally share.
It's been such a ride, and we are honored to have been working with great artists @malec3821 @Max Maleo

Each one put his heart to give his best, so we hope you like it as much as we do!!

Credits:
Animatic by Malec and Max Maleo 
Animation, clean up and vfx by Eddie Mehong, Max Maleo, Malec
Ink & paint by Max Mleo & Eddie Mehond
Layout by Max maleo
Backgrounds by Antoine Bertrand
Music By Matt Collins
SFX by Game Audio Factory
